     <div type="poem" subtype="to_the__reader">
   <pb facs="4"/>
   <head>A caueat to the Reader.</head>
   <l>HEnce Venus idle ympes, hence, hence in haste,</l>
   <l>Here is no place for Cupids fancies blinde:</l>
   <l>All wanton eyes and eares which are vnchaste,</l>
   <l>Are here vnlike their bace content to finde:</l>
   <l>For only such as vertue haue imbraste:</l>
   <l>May here learne how to loue, to liue, to dye,</l>
   <l>And after death to scale the loftie skye.</l>
</div>
